___
### [choco://keepass-browser-importer](choco://keepass-browser-importer)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [(unofficial) choco:// Protocol support ](https://chocolatey.org/packages/choco-protocol-support)
___
KeePassBrowserImporter is a plug-in for [_KeePass 2.x_](http://www.KeePass.info) which lets you import credentials from various browsers.
